  "root_text": {
    "sn2.14:0.1": "Saṁyutta Nikāya 2.14 ",
    "sn2.14:0.2": "2. Anāthapiṇḍikavagga ",
    "sn2.14:0.3": "Nandanasutta ",
    "sn2.14:1.1": "Ekamantaṁ ṭhito kho nandano devaputto bhagavantaṁ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: ",
    "sn2.14:2.1": "“Pucchāmi taṁ gotama bhūripañña, ",
    "sn2.14:2.2": "Anāvaṭaṁ bhagavato ñāṇadassanaṁ; ",
    "sn2.14:2.3": "Kathaṁvidhaṁ sīlavantaṁ vadanti, ",
    "sn2.14:2.4": "Kathaṁvidhaṁ paññavantaṁ vadanti; ",
    "sn2.14:2.5": "Kathaṁvidho dukkhamaticca iriyati, ",
    "sn2.14:2.6": "Kathaṁvidhaṁ devatā pūjayantī”ti. ",
    "sn2.14:3.1": "“Yo sīlavā paññavā bhāvitatto, ",
    "sn2.14:3.2": "Samāhito jhānarato satīmā; ",
    "sn2.14:3.3": "Sabbassa sokā vigatā pahīnā, ",
    "sn2.14:3.4": "Khīṇāsavo antimadehadhārī. ",
    "sn2.14:4.1": "Tathāvidhaṁ sīlavantaṁ vadanti, ",
    "sn2.14:4.2": "Tathāvidhaṁ paññavantaṁ vadanti; ",
    "sn2.14:4.3": "Tathāvidho dukkhamaticca iriyati, ",
    "sn2.14:4.4": "Tathāvidhaṁ devatā pūjayantī”ti. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "sn2.14:0.1": "Linked Discourses 2.14 ",
    "sn2.14:0.2": "2. With Anāthapiṇḍika ",
    "sn2.14:0.3": "With Nandana ",
    "sn2.14:1.1": "Standing to one side, the godling Nandana addressed the Buddha in verse: ",
    "sn2.14:2.1": "“I ask you, Gotama, whose wisdom is vast, ",
    "sn2.14:2.2": "the Blessed One <j>of unhindered knowledge and vision. ",
    "sn2.14:2.3": "What sort do they call ethical? ",
    "sn2.14:2.4": "What sort do they call wise? ",
    "sn2.14:2.5": "What sort lives on after transcending suffering? ",
    "sn2.14:2.6": "What sort is worshipped by the deities?” ",
    "sn2.14:3.1": "“Someone who is ethical, wise, evolved, ",
    "sn2.14:3.2": "becomes serene, loving absorption, mindful, ",
    "sn2.14:3.3": "who’s gotten rid of and given up all sorrows, ",
    "sn2.14:3.4": "with defilements ended, they bear their final body. ",
    "sn2.14:4.1": "That sort they call ethical. ",
    "sn2.14:4.2": "That sort they call wise. ",
    "sn2.14:4.3": "That sort lives on after transcending suffering. ",
    "sn2.14:4.4": "That sort is worshipped by the deities.” "
  },
